<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Siempa Pathien in lei danin,
 Ma a Ana siem chu;
 Pasal changa um phal loin,
 Panpih ding A siem tai.

[V2]
 Lawpin chawian hitiu,
 Kichenna thiengtho hi,
 Khen loh thim thu a tiem u hi,
 Nangma'n vang hun pien la.

[V3]
 2. Lungkham leh buoina a thawk un,
 Nangman thawkpih zelin;
 A chung u ah ni bang vakin,
 Vangsakna'n hun vukin.

[V4]
 3. Na min loin thu a tiem tau
 Nangman na hetpih in;
 Khenlohna khut a suih u hi,
 Kanin, hehpih gui in.</lyrics>
<title>Kichenna Thiengtho</title>
<hymn_number>259</hymn_number>
<author>Upa Rokunga</author>
</song>